title: NFL ATL: NFC Camp Preview, Pt. 1
itunes:title: NFL ATL: NFC Camp Preview, Pt. 1
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Kevin Patra -- break down the latest news from around the NFL including Jamaal Charles' new contract, Sidney Rice's retirement and much more. Chris Wesseling also calls in for part one of an NFC training camp preview, highlighting teams from the NFC East and NFC West.
